EULA J. NEILSON, a single woman, v. BILL BLYTHE 31 So. (2nd) 64

June Term, 1947

June 24, 1947 Division B W. F. Finch and R. C. Prescott, for appellant. J. R. Bullock, for appellee. PER CURIAM:

The decree is affirmed upon authority of McKinney v. Gainey, 96 Fla. 547, 118 So. 917 and Smith et al. v. Hope et al., 47 Fla. 295, 35 So. 865.

Affirmed.

THOMAS, C. J., BUFORD, ADAMS and BARNS, JJ., concur.
